    "result": {"data":{"allStrapiBooks":{"nodes":[{"slug":"a-brief-history-of-humankind","title":"人类简史","author":"[以色列] 尤瓦尔·赫拉利","description":"尤瓦尔·赫拉利，1976年生，牛津大学历史学博士，现为耶路撒冷希伯来大学的历史系教授，青年怪才，全球瞩目的新锐历史学家，擅长世界历史和宏观历史进程研究，在学术领域和大众出版领域都有很大的兴趣。《人类简史》一书让他一举成名，成为以色列超级畅销书，目前这本书已授20多个国家版权，在历史学之外，人类学、生态学、基因学等领域的知识信手拈来。\n","rank":50,"published_at":"2022-01-03T08:13:41.000Z","image":{"localFile":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","backgroundColor":"#d8d8d8","images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/1c1e53528ded0ffcd368a7c3b6cea847/3212f/_2a5eb5bbba.jpg","srcSet":"/static/1c1e53528ded0ffcd368a7c3b6cea847/5c809/_2a5eb5bbba.jpg 25w,\n/static/1c1e53528ded0ffcd368a7c3b6cea847/5c9f3/_2a5eb5bbba.jpg 50w,\n/static/1c1e53528ded0ffcd368a7c3b6cea847/3212f/_2a5eb5bbba.jpg 100w,\n/static/1c1e53528ded0ffcd368a7c3b6cea847/291ee/_2a5eb5bbba.jpg 200w","sizes":"(min-width: 100px) 100px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/1c1e53528ded0ffcd368a7c3b6cea847/7f5c9/_2a5eb5bbba.webp 25w,\n/static/1c1e53528ded0ffcd368a7c3b6cea847/de8f1/_2a5eb5bbba.webp 50w,\n/static/1c1e53528ded0ffcd368a7c3b6cea847/fd5fd/_2a5eb5bbba.webp 100w,\n/static/1c1e53528ded0ffcd368a7c3b6cea847/436db/_2a5eb5bbba.webp 200w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 100px) 100px, 100vw"}]},"width":100,"height":140}}}}},{"slug":"bnlfmxs","title":"别闹了，费曼先生","author":"[美] 理查德·费曼","description":"费曼得过诺贝尔奖，是现代最伟大的理论物理学家之一。但他同时也可能是历史上唯一被按摩院请去画裸体画、偷偷打开放着原子弹机密文件的保险箱，在巴西桑巴乐团担任鼓手的科学家。他曾跟爱因斯坦和波尔等大师讨论物理问题，也曾在赌城跟职业赌徒研究输赢机率。\n","rank":50,"published_at":"2022-01-16T04:31:40.000Z","image":{"localFile":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","backgroundColor":"#f8f8f8","images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/7e5a2d290d6dd88cd9fd47725c524471/3212f/_6fadc4785b.jpg","srcSet":"/static/7e5a2d290d6dd88cd9fd47725c524471/5c809/_6fadc4785b.jpg 25w,\n/static/7e5a2d290d6dd88cd9fd47725c524471/5c9f3/_6fadc4785b.jpg 50w,\n/static/7e5a2d290d6dd88cd9fd47725c524471/3212f/_6fadc4785b.jpg 100w,\n/static/7e5a2d290d6dd88cd9fd47725c524471/291ee/_6fadc4785b.jpg 200w","sizes":"(min-width: 100px) 100px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/7e5a2d290d6dd88cd9fd47725c524471/7f5c9/_6fadc4785b.webp 25w,\n/static/7e5a2d290d6dd88cd9fd47725c524471/de8f1/_6fadc4785b.webp 50w,\n/static/7e5a2d290d6dd88cd9fd47725c524471/fd5fd/_6fadc4785b.webp 100w,\n/static/7e5a2d290d6dd88cd9fd47725c524471/436db/_6fadc4785b.webp 200w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 100px) 100px, 100vw"}]},"width":100,"height":140}}}}},{"slug":"a-brief-history-of-time","title":"时间简史","author":"[英] 史蒂芬·霍金|","description":"《时间简史》讲述是探索时间和空间核心秘密的故事，是关于宇宙本性的最前沿知识，包括我们的宇宙图像、空间和时间、膨胀的宇宙不确定性原理、基本粒子和自然的力、黑洞、黑洞不是这么黑、时间箭头等内容。第一版中的许多理论预言，后来在对微观或宏观宇宙世界观测中得到证实。\n\n自1988年首版以来，《时间简史》已成为全球科学著作的里程碑。它被翻译成40种文字，销售了近1000万册。此版更新了内容，把许多观测揭示的新知识，以及霍金最新的研究纳入，并配以250幅照片和电脑制作的三维和四维空间图。","rank":50,"published_at":"2022-01-15T16:41:29.000Z","image":{"localFile":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","backgroundColor":"#181818","images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/40b9dbb981c64705bd94c1adc4f4bd02/3212f/_28c578e85d.jpg","srcSet":"/static/40b9dbb981c64705bd94c1adc4f4bd02/5c809/_28c578e85d.jpg 25w,\n/static/40b9dbb981c64705bd94c1adc4f4bd02/5c9f3/_28c578e85d.jpg 50w,\n/static/40b9dbb981c64705bd94c1adc4f4bd02/3212f/_28c578e85d.jpg 100w,\n/static/40b9dbb981c64705bd94c1adc4f4bd02/291ee/_28c578e85d.jpg 200w","sizes":"(min-width: 100px) 100px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/40b9dbb981c64705bd94c1adc4f4bd02/7f5c9/_28c578e85d.webp 25w,\n/static/40b9dbb981c64705bd94c1adc4f4bd02/de8f1/_28c578e85d.webp 50w,\n/static/40b9dbb981c64705bd94c1adc4f4bd02/fd5fd/_28c578e85d.webp 100w,\n/static/40b9dbb981c64705bd94c1adc4f4bd02/436db/_28c578e85d.webp 200w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 100px) 100px, 100vw"}]},"width":100,"height":140}}}}},{"slug":"zhdgb","title":"最好的告别","author":"[美] 阿图·葛文德","description":"当独立、自助的生活不能再维持时，我们该怎么办？在生命临近终点的时刻，我们该和医生谈些什么？应该如何优雅地跨越生命的终点？对于这些问题，大多数人缺少清晰的观念，而只是把命运交由医学、技术和陌生人来掌控。影响世界的医生阿图•葛文德结合其多年的外科医生经验与流畅的文笔，讲述了一个个伤感而发人深省的故事，对在21世纪变老意味着什么进行了清醒、深入的探索。本书富有洞见、感人至深，并为我们提供了实用的路线图，告诉我们为了使生命最后的岁月有意义，我们可以做什么、应该做什么。","rank":50,"published_at":"2022-01-15T16:13:07.000Z","image":{"localFile":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","backgroundColor":"#f8e8c8","images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/336bc91ec3ed830cd6b0cbe34672e3e4/3212f/_3e1077dc99.jpg","srcSet":"/static/336bc91ec3ed830cd6b0cbe34672e3e4/5c809/_3e1077dc99.jpg 25w,\n/static/336bc91ec3ed830cd6b0cbe34672e3e4/5c9f3/_3e1077dc99.jpg 50w,\n/static/336bc91ec3ed830cd6b0cbe34672e3e4/3212f/_3e1077dc99.jpg 100w,\n/static/336bc91ec3ed830cd6b0cbe34672e3e4/291ee/_3e1077dc99.jpg 200w","sizes":"(min-width: 100px) 100px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/336bc91ec3ed830cd6b0cbe34672e3e4/7f5c9/_3e1077dc99.webp 25w,\n/static/336bc91ec3ed830cd6b0cbe34672e3e4/de8f1/_3e1077dc99.webp 50w,\n/static/336bc91ec3ed830cd6b0cbe34672e3e4/fd5fd/_3e1077dc99.webp 100w,\n/static/336bc91ec3ed830cd6b0cbe34672e3e4/436db/_3e1077dc99.webp 200w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 100px) 100px, 100vw"}]},"width":100,"height":140}}}}},{"slug":"cydwqd","title":"从一到无穷大","author":"[美] 乔治·伽莫夫","description":"本书是最负盛名的世界科普经典著作之一，它曾引领千千万万的读者进入科学世界。许多人都是因为在十几岁的时候读到这本书，才第一次真正领略了科学的奇迹和奥秘。作者以其幽默的笔调和高超的教学技巧，探讨了宏观世界和微观世界、数论、空间和时间的相对性、熵、基因、原子结构、核裂变和太阳系的起源等主题。无论你的科学知识水平如何，你都会从这本不同寻常的书中获得许多乐趣和激励。它是任何对科学世界充满好奇的人的必读书。","rank":50,"published_at":"2022-01-15T16:02:30.000Z","image":{"localFile":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","backgroundColor":"#386888","images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/164bb4c33b06c7c0086dbe8b6e36c5b8/3212f/_101a1972df.jpg","srcSet":"/static/164bb4c33b06c7c0086dbe8b6e36c5b8/5c809/_101a1972df.jpg 25w,\n/static/164bb4c33b06c7c0086dbe8b6e36c5b8/5c9f3/_101a1972df.jpg 50w,\n/static/164bb4c33b06c7c0086dbe8b6e36c5b8/3212f/_101a1972df.jpg 100w,\n/static/164bb4c33b06c7c0086dbe8b6e36c5b8/291ee/_101a1972df.jpg 200w","sizes":"(min-width: 100px) 100px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/164bb4c33b06c7c0086dbe8b6e36c5b8/7f5c9/_101a1972df.webp 25w,\n/static/164bb4c33b06c7c0086dbe8b6e36c5b8/de8f1/_101a1972df.webp 50w,\n/static/164bb4c33b06c7c0086dbe8b6e36c5b8/fd5fd/_101a1972df.webp 100w,\n/static/164bb4c33b06c7c0086dbe8b6e36c5b8/436db/_101a1972df.webp 200w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 100px) 100px, 100vw"}]},"width":100,"height":140}}}}},{"slug":"sdztzm","title":"上帝掷骰子吗","author":"曹天元","description":"这本书是关于量子论的故事。量子论是一个极为奇妙的理论：从物理角度来说，它在科学家中间引起了最为激烈的争议和关注；从现实角度来说，它给我们的社会带来了无与伦比的变化和进步；从科学史角度来说，也几乎没有哪段历史比量子论的创立得到了更为彻底的研究。然而不可思议的是，它的基本观点和假说至今没有渗透到大众的意识中去，这无疑又给它增添了一道神秘的光环。","rank":50,"published_at":"2022-01-15T15:46:14.000Z","image":{"localFile":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","backgroundColor":"#080808","images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/947c77ec2bfe4056d42e7b9838e3bafb/3212f/_024ff6ec09.jpg","srcSet":"/static/947c77ec2bfe4056d42e7b9838e3bafb/5c809/_024ff6ec09.jpg 25w,\n/static/947c77ec2bfe4056d42e7b9838e3bafb/5c9f3/_024ff6ec09.jpg 50w,\n/static/947c77ec2bfe4056d42e7b9838e3bafb/3212f/_024ff6ec09.jpg 100w,\n/static/947c77ec2bfe4056d42e7b9838e3bafb/291ee/_024ff6ec09.jpg 200w","sizes":"(min-width: 100px) 100px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/947c77ec2bfe4056d42e7b9838e3bafb/7f5c9/_024ff6ec09.webp 25w,\n/static/947c77ec2bfe4056d42e7b9838e3bafb/de8f1/_024ff6ec09.webp 50w,\n/static/947c77ec2bfe4056d42e7b9838e3bafb/fd5fd/_024ff6ec09.webp 100w,\n/static/947c77ec2bfe4056d42e7b9838e3bafb/436db/_024ff6ec09.webp 200w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 100px) 100px, 100vw"}]},"width":100,"height":140}}}}}]},"strapiBookTags":{"name":"科普","slug":"science"},"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"收集优质资源","author":"@learn-anything.cn","description":"追求极简语言，说明事物因果！","email":"lh@learn-anything.cn"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"science","pageSize":24,"total":6,"numPages":1,"currentPage":1,"skip":0}},
